{"about_the_game":"The rules of World Soccer Kid are very simple.<br />\r\nMove Soccer Kid to juggle the ball with your head.<br />\r\nBut the further from the center of the head the ball hits, the further the ball moves, making it hard to juggle.<br />\r\nThere are 4 modes that use these simple rules.<br />\r\nBasic Mode where the number of juggles is recorded, Running Mode where the distance moved while juggling is recorded, Two-Player Mode where you compete against an opponent to juggle the ball the longest, and Two-Player Coop Mode where you work together to record how many times you can juggle the ball.<br />\r\nPractice hard and try to become the best Soccer Kid in the world!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhen playing local multiplayer<br />\r\n(Game Pad)<br />\r\nPlayer 1 : A button - Change direction, B button - Jump<br />\r\nPlayer 2 : A button - Change direction, B button - Jump<br />\r\n<br />\r\n(Keyboard)<br />\r\nPlayer 1 : S  - Change direction W or A or D - Jump<br />\r\nPlayer 1 : K  - Change direction I or J or L - Jump","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2252170?t=1672993140","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252170/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1672993140","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252170/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1672993140","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2252170/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1672993140","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],